$\tilde{w}$ grows exponentially. Figure (b) shows a plot of
$F^q_{asym}(\nu,\tilde{w})$. The figure shows that the limit of of the
integral at $\tilde{w}\to\infty$ is reached very fast. In the limit of
$\tilde{w}\to\infty$ we know the integral exactly.}
